Kanika Racemenu Preset

Extract the nif and dds files to your Data/SKSE/Plugins/CharGen folder
Extract the jslot file to your Data/SKSE/Plugins folder

This character is based off the nord race. Make sure to set weight to 1

This preset uses the following mods:
Eyes of Beauty
KS Hairdos
SG Female Textures Renewal

Screenshots taken using Tetrachromatic and not enhanced with photoshop or any image editing software.
